                          <p class="Para">In this paper we will discuss the software engineering technology for the 21<sup>st</sup> century.</p>
                          <p class="Para">First we review development over the last half-century, overview application requirement and environment, accept a challenge.</p>
                          <p class="Para">The we outline following software engineering techniques: 1) Process; 2) Analysis; 3) Design; 4) UML; 5) Component; 6) Java +XML; 7) Integrated;, 8) Quality (ISO9000&amp;CMM).</p>
